se from the analysis of Helmholtz energies.\nAdditionally, we show the evolution of the spectrum of 1D boron nitride (BN) to\ndemonstrate that GF2 is capable of qualitatively describing the temperature\neffects influencing the size of the band gap.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 May 2016 23:57:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Jun 2016 05:33:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 28 Oct 2016 15:45:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-24"}
