l flank of IP-shock and\npropagating radially outward from location of the solar eruption. We also\nconfirmed the average $G_z$ changing its sign above and below the heliospheric\ncurrent sheet, in accord with the prediction of the drift model for the\nlarge-scale GCR transport in the heliosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 21 May 2016 05:55:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-13"}
